room_title: Escape room "Cursed Cabin" by Lockdown Escape Rooms in Las Vegas
room_address: 6376 W Sahara Ave. Las Vegas, NV 89146
room_description:
Many rumors have circulated about the strange woman Sanguina who lives on the outskirts of town. Apparently, all who visit her house are never seen again. Unable to quiet your curiosity, you and your friends break in on a dare.
Once inside, it’s clear that the cabin belongs to no ordinary woman, but a witch! The doors and windows have been magically barred – you know Sanguina will return in one hour; you’ve got to escape before she finds you here!
